### 🔸 Summary of Key Concepts

| Object | Purpose |
|-------|--------|
| `BattleManager` | Controls the flow of battle, turn order, and state |
| `BattleCharacter` | Base class for player and enemy characters |
| `Skill` | Magic or special abilities |
| `Item` | Healing potions, scrolls, etc. |
| `BattleAction` | Represents what a character does on their turn |
| `BattleActionType` | Enum to categorize actions |

